entries.journal_entry_description: Boba has passed on some Bounty targets for you to complete. Do so, and return to him for your reward.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Ratheb knows where Fidaval is, you must 'convince' him to tell you where to find him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Speak with Ratheb in the Cantina
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to head up to the Atrium.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Atrium
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Now that you know where he is hiding, take him down. Be careful, he may have bodyguards.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good work, you did better than I expected. I have another job for you. Retrieve a datapad from Arslynd. Take it from him, and make sure he isn't capable of telling anyone about it later.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Arslynd has some information that Boba Fett needs on a certain shipment. Collect that information by any means necessary.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Now that you have completed your task, use the elevator to return to the main level.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Main Level
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: You have taken out your mark, now return to Boba Fett.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Return to Boba Fett in the Cantina
